{
  "info": {
    "name": "Passlify Core Service API",
    "description": "All endpoints of passlify-core-service.\n\n## Setup\n1. Start infra: `docker compose -f ci/docker-compose.yml up -d` (Postgres + Keycloak + Mailpit).\n2. Start the app: `./mvnw spring-boot:run` (listens on :8081).\n3. In this collection, open **Auth → Get Token** and Send — it logs into Keycloak (user `organizer1` by default) and saves the JWT into the `token` collection variable. All authenticated requests inherit it automatically.\n\n## Roles\nAny authenticated user can create/manage their own events (they become the organizer via ownership — no special role). Switch the `username` collection variable to exercise the role-gated areas (all password `password`):\n- `organizer1` → a regular user; can organize events + buy tickets\n- `operator1` → OPERATOR (scanning)\n- `admin1` → ADMIN (everything, incl. list all organizations)\n\nPaid events require a COMPANY profile first — see the **Organization** folder.\n\n## Chaining\nCreate requests save their generated ids into collection variables (`eventId`, `ticketTypeId`, `orderId`, `customFieldId`, `sessionId`, `ticketId`), so you can run folders top-to-bottom. Public/guest/webhook requests use No Auth (the resource UUID or a signature is the capability).\n\nInteractive docs also live at http://localhost:8081/swagger-ui.html",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081" },
    { "key": "keycloakUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "realm", "value": "passlify" },
    { "key": "clientId", "value": "passlify-client" },
    { "key": "username", "value": "organizer1" },
    { "key": "password", "value": "password" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "eventId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "slug", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ticketTypeId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "customFieldId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "ticketId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "sessionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "provider", "value": "mock" },
    { "key": "qrToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Token (Keycloak)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('got access_token', () => pm.expect(json.access_token).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "grant_type", "value": "password" },
                { "key": "client_id", "value": "{{clientId}}" },
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{username}}" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{password}}" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{keycloakUrl}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "host": ["{{keycloakUrl}}"],
              "path": ["realms", "{{realm}}", "protocol", "openid-connect", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Direct Access Grant against Keycloak. Saves access_token → {{token}}. Change the `username` collection variable to operator1 / admin1 for other roles."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Public Catalog (no auth)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Browse events",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/events?q=&city=&page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "public", "events"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "q", "value": "", "description": "free-text search", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "city", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "eventType", "value": "", "description": "event type UUID", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "from", "value": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z", "description": "ISO-8601 instant", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "to", "value": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get published event by slug",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/events/{{slug}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "public", "events", "{{slug}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List event types (catalog)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/public/event-types",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "public", "event-types"]
            },
            "description": "Active event types: non-selectable category parents + selectable leaves. Pick a leaf id for an event's eventTypeId."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Organization (my profile)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get my organization",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/organization",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "me", "organization"]
            },
            "description": "Your organizer profile. 404 until you create an event (auto-creates an INDIVIDUAL profile) or PUT one below."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upsert my organization (COMPANY)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"kind\": \"COMPANY\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Startit Events d.o.o.\",\n  \"legalName\": \"Startit Events d.o.o. Beograd\",\n  \"vatPib\": \"123456789\",\n  \"registrationNo\": \"21234567\",\n  \"addressLine\": \"Savska 5\",\n  \"city\": \"Belgrade\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"11000\",\n  \"country\": \"RS\",\n  \"contactEmail\": \"billing@startit.rs\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/organization",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "me", "organization"]
            },
            "description": "Required before publishing a PAID event. For a free-only organizer, send {\"kind\":\"INDIVIDUAL\",\"displayName\":\"...\"}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Admin: list all organizations",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/organizations?page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "admin", "organizations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "ADMIN only — set username=admin1 and re-run Get Token."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Events (any authenticated user)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create event",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('eventId', j.id);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('slug', j.slug);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Belgrade Tech Meetup\",\n  \"descriptionHtml\": \"<p>An evening of <b>talks</b> and networking.</p>\",\n  \"coverImageUrl\": \"https://example.com/cover.jpg\",\n  \"startsAt\": \"2026-09-01T18:00:00Z\",\n  \"endsAt\": \"2026-09-01T22:00:00Z\",\n  \"timezone\": \"Europe/Belgrade\",\n  \"attendanceMode\": \"IN_PERSON\",\n  \"commercialMode\": \"PAID\",\n  \"capacity\": 200,\n  \"tags\": [\"tech\", \"networking\"],\n  \"currency\": \"RSD\",\n  \"visibility\": \"PUBLIC\",\n  \"paymentProvider\": \"MOCK\",\n  \"location\": {\n    \"name\": \"Startit Centar\",\n    \"city\": \"Belgrade\",\n    \"address\": \"Savska 5\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events"]
            },
            "description": "name, startsAt, endsAt, timezone (IANA) are required. descriptionHtml is sanitized server-side. attendanceMode (IN_PERSON default), commercialMode (FREE default; FREE forces paymentProvider=NONE), currency/paymentProvider/visibility fall back to defaults if omitted. Provide `location` (create-or-reuse) OR `locationId` (reuse) OR neither."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List my events",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events?status=&page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "DRAFT", "description": "DRAFT|PUBLISHED|COMPLETED|CANCELLED", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get event",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update event",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Belgrade Tech Meetup (Autumn)\",\n  \"capacity\": 250\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Partial update — only non-null fields are applied."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Publication readiness",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/publication-readiness",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "publication-readiness"]
            },
            "description": "Structured checklist of what is still missing before the event can be published."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Publish event",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/publish",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "publish"]
            },
            "description": "One-way. Requires at least one active ticket type (paid → COMPANY profile + provider)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete event",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/complete",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "complete"]
            },
            "description": "Published → Completed."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel event",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"The venue is no longer available.\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/cancel",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "cancel"]
            },
            "description": "Reason is required and recorded in the audit trail."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get event settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/settings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "settings"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update event settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"minimumAge\": 18,\n  \"ticketsAvailableAtEntrance\": true,\n  \"visitorCountryRestrictionEnabled\": false,\n  \"multipleEntryAllowed\": false,\n  \"peopleWithDisabilitiesFreeEntry\": true,\n  \"childrenFreeEntryAge\": 7,\n  \"termsHtml\": \"<p>Be respectful.</p>\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/settings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "settings"]
            },
            "description": "Full replace. If visitorCountryRestrictionEnabled is true, allowedVisitorCountryCodes (ISO alpha-2) must be non-empty."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update online access",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"publicUrl\": \"https://meet.example.com/passlify\",\n  \"platformName\": \"Google Meet\",\n  \"accessInstructionsHtml\": \"<p>Join 10 minutes early.</p>\",\n  \"revealOnlyAfterRegistration\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/online-access",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "online-access"]
            },
            "description": "For ONLINE / HYBRID events. Join URL must be https."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Event audit trail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/audit",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "audit"]
            },
            "description": "Reverse-chronological audit history of the event."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Collaborators (event-scoped)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List collaborators",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/collaborators",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "collaborators"]
            },
            "description": "Owner / admin / manager only."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Invite collaborator",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": ["const b = pm.response.json();", "pm.collectionVariables.set('collaboratorId', b.id);", "pm.collectionVariables.set('inviteToken', b.acceptToken);"]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"colleague@example.com\",\n  \"role\": \"EDITOR\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/collaborators",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "collaborators"]
            },
            "description": "role: MANAGER|EDITOR|VIEWER|CHECK_IN_OPERATOR (OWNER is not assignable). Saves id → collaboratorId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Accept invitation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{inviteToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/collaborators/accept",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "collaborators", "accept"]
            },
            "description": "Called by the invitee (token from the invite email; their account email must match)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change collaborator role",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"VIEWER\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/collaborators/{{collaboratorId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "collaborators", "{{collaboratorId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Remove collaborator",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/collaborators/{{collaboratorId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "collaborators", "{{collaboratorId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Transfer ownership",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"targetCollaboratorId\": \"{{collaboratorId}}\",\n  \"confirm\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}/transfer-ownership",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "events", "{{eventId}}", "transfer-ownership"]
            },
            "description": "Owner/admin only. Target must be an accepted collaborator; the previous owner becomes MANAGER."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
